B.X2=new A.aj("Su, insan v\xfccudunun y\xfczde 60'\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015fturan ve neredeyse t\xfcm metabolik s\xfcre\xe7lerin temelini olu\u015fturan vazge\xe7ilmez bir bile\u015fendir. Besin maddelerini ta\u015f\u0131mak, v\xfccut \u0131s\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 d\xfczenlemek, eklemleri ya\u011flamak, at\u0131k maddeleri uzakla\u015ft\u0131rmak ve biyokimyasal reaksiyonlara ortam haz\u0131rlamak suyun ba\u015fl\u0131ca g\xf6revleri aras\u0131ndad\u0131r. Yeterli su t\xfcketimi, hem sa\u011fl\u0131k hem de fiziksel performans a\xe7\u0131s\u0131ndan kalori ya da protein kadar kritik \xf6neme sahiptir.\n\nG\xfcnl\xfck su ihtiyac\u0131 ki\u015fiden ki\u015fiye \xf6nemli \xf6l\xe7\xfcde de\u011fi\u015fir. Bu hesap makinesi, v\xfccut a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z\u0131, aktivite d\xfczeyinizi ve iklim ko\u015fullar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 birlikte de\u011ferlendirerek ki\u015fiselle\u015ftirilmi\u015f bir tavsiye sunar. Yayg\u0131n kullan\u0131lan temel form\xfcl; v\xfccut a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131n kilogram\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131na 30-35 ml su olarak hesaplanmas\u0131d\u0131r. Buna g\xf6re 70 kg bir birey i\xe7in g\xfcnl\xfck temel su ihtiyac\u0131 2.1-2.45 litre olarak belirlenir.\n\nEgzersiz, su ihtiyac\u0131n\u0131 \xf6nemli \xf6l\xe7\xfcde art\u0131r\u0131r. Egzersiz s\u0131ras\u0131nda kaybedilen s\u0131v\u0131y\u0131 yerine koymak i\xe7in her 30 dakikal\u0131k aktivite i\xe7in su t\xfcketimini art\u0131rmak \xf6nemlidir.",null,B.B0,null,null,null,null,null)
